Boost performance:
export TF_XLA_FLAGS="--tf_xla_auto_jit=2"
export TF_CPP_MIN_LOG_LEVEL=2

This enables XLA compilation and cleaner logs

Set up SSH keys

Using key authentication
On host:
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "kgiri@uwyo" -f ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
This will create private and public key

Copy the public key to Remote Nodes

cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub | ssh kgiri@mteverest1.uwyo.edu 'mkdir -p ~/.ssh && cat >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys && chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys'

Copy to your own authorized_keys
cat ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
